    {
      "id": "NG3pR1ZkvA-MzL7nfu-xk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3295.0288500380157,
      "y": -1987.269834246651,
      "width": 523.3396606445312,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1915080845,
      "version": 1150,
      "versionNonce": 828251728,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774176853098,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Outlets and data points are different and the cables\nare part of each kit. They all make a kit.\n\nKit: this is the final product, the assembly of multiple\nmaterials, an outlet with stuff in it. Then a kit of\ndata points with its components\n\nThe different products are end points(anything that\nhas contact with electricity) e.g;\n\ni) a light endpoint\nii) an outlet is an endpoint\nii) washing machine endpoint\n\nall these make separate kits",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "AZJFttxOLPSMhGUnowQjY",
      "originalText": "Outlets and data points are different and the cables are part of each kit. They all make a kit.\n\nKit: this is the final product, the assembly of multiple materials, an outlet with stuff in it. Then a kit of data points with its components\n\nThe different products are end points(anything that has contact with electricity) e.g;\n\ni) a light endpoint\nii) an outlet is an endpoint\nii) washing machine endpoint\n\nall these make separate kits",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0d",
      "autoResize": true
    },
